This is a monster tour now - such growth! Over a million here & it's still growing like a boom town. One can ride twenty miles or more in the city & not twice! The trines took me for a drive through Topango Canyon & down along the sea night before last. Took bunch along & couldn't find a place to eat it, so brought it back & ate it. in their room! This evening I have to be with the Bookfellows here - Los Angeles branch. Don't want to go at all, but got roped in like a simpleton. Have been dad <unclear/> social engagements with fair success. 

